      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; equivalency between experimental and simulation inputs reviewed qualitatively.",
      "rationale": "Qualitative review confirms that CFD boundary conditions are consistent with experimental measurements. Formal equivalency analysis is not required at MRL 2 for this comparative device assessment."
